prompts.frontCover:
A full-body, 2D watercolor illustration of a young, smiling couple, Lao Lao and Jordan, based on the reference photo. The style is lighthearted and humorous, with slightly exaggerated features for comic effect. Lao Lao, a young East Asian woman with long, straight dark hair and round wire-frame glasses, is wearing a light blue sweatshirt (with logos omitted) and black pants. Jordan, a young Southeast Asian man with short, dark, textured hair, is standing behind her, wearing a tan hoodie and dark reddish-brown pants. In a funny twist, Jordan is shown lifting Lao Lao off the ground in a big bear hug from behind, as if she weighs nothing, while she has a surprised and delighted expression, kicking her feet playfully in the air. The background is a simplified, soft-focus watercolor wash of a serene lake and a cloudy sky, with subtle hints of a distant shoreline. The entire scene has a beautiful, artistic watercolor feel with visible paper texture, soft color bleeds, and delicate brushstrokes.

Centered in a clear space, the text reads "Happy Birthday to my favorite person to pick on!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
